{"type": "article", "id": 30104, "title": "可以放花草的灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-25T23:06:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160725212411bEJM89PoBXnp7hFx.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>你的床头灯也能变成展示花草的家饰，波兰设计工作室 Lightovo 推出的 Milo Lamp 就是一款能够摆放花器的灯具，不仅可以放在桌上也可以当作吊灯使用。金属灯罩下方连接着一个玻璃罩子，两边各有一个小洞，通过它可以塞入不大的花草，浇起水来也非常方便。简洁的造型适用于各种居家环境，温暖的灯光与绿意盎然的植物相结合，带给人一种平和舒适的感觉。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/Lightovo\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 201.69 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725212520gNP1DIwOe9SKUABv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.318750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725212520AzHOPZ4IwMWTbc5N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.462500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016072521254462CZKnWosMQgHJvy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.280000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}